SSConverter is a Perl project for converting CSV files to XLS files

-------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
1.  perl -MCPAN -e shell
    cpan> install Spreadsheet::WriteExcel
    cpan> install Excel::Writer::XLSX
2.  git clone git@github.com/absperf/ssconverter
3.  cd ssconverter
4.  cp ssconverter.pl /usr/local/bin
5.  put it in cron
    * * * * * /usr/local/bin/ssconverter.pl /dir_to_watch /dir_to_write

